10a4 7e			      ld    A, (HL) 
10a5 23			      inc   HL 
10a6 b6			      or    (HL) 
10a7 c2 4f 11		      jp    NZ, free_done 
10aa			 
10aa 2b			      dec   HL 
10ab			 
10ab 44			      ld    B, H                    ; Copy HL to BC 
10ac 4d			      ld    C, L 
10ad			 
