# End of macro CWHEAD
1d9d			; | HEAP ( -- u1 u2 )   Pushes u1 the current number of bytes in the heap and u2 the remaining bytes - Only present if using my MALLOC | DONE 
1d9d			; | | u1 - Current number of bytes in the heap 
1d9d			; | | u2 - Remaining bytes left on the heap 
1d9d			; | |  
