4428			 
4428					NEXTW 
4428			 
4428			.TLOAD: 
4428				CWHEAD .TCAL 31 "LOAD" 4 WORD_FLAG_CODE 
4428			; | LOAD ( n -- )    Load file n from tape and exec | TO DO 
